                </p>
                <p>    			
                    Iṭaiyāṟṟu-nāṭṭu-t tiru-t-tava-t-tuṟai <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>va<unclear>rkku</unclear>
                    <lb n="2"/>I<choice><orig>ñ-ñ</orig><reg>n-n</reg></choice>āṭṭu kavira-p-poṟ-kaṭṭiyūr-Uṭaiyāṉ pūti kaṇṭaṉ ci<unclear>t</unclear>tirai-vi<hi rend="grantha">ṣu</hi> tiru-viḻāvukku tāyārai-c cārtti v<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ai</corr></choice>tta poṉ <unclear>pati</unclear>
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>ṉ kaḻ<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ai</corr></choice>ñc’ arai
                </p>
                <p>    			
                    Ip-poṉ patiṉ kaḻ<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ai</corr></choice>ñc’ arai poṉṉuṅ I<choice><orig><unclear>ñ</unclear>-ñ</orig><reg>n-n</reg></choice>āṭṭu muttaiyil <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yōṅ koṇṭu ca<choice><orig>ṉ</orig><reg>n</reg></choice><unclear>tirātittava</unclear>
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>Āṭṭāṇṭu-toṟuñ cittirai-vi<hi rend="grantha">ṣu</hi> tiru-viḻāvukku nārāya-n<unclear>āḻi</unclear>yāl Eḻu nāḷaikkum nicati kalavarai Arici patt-e<unclear>ṭṭu-k kuttal</unclear>
                    <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">ma</supplied>ṭāvil Aṭṭum paricē Eḻu nāḷ muṉt’ uṟa <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-kōyilukkē <unclear>koṇ</unclear>ṭu ceṉṟu Aḷappōm āṉōm
                </p>
                <p>
                    Aḷavōmāyi<unclear>l muṭṭ’ ira</unclear>
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ṭṭi</supplied> <hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvarar·</hi> taṇṭi-k-koḷḷa Oṭṭi-k kuṭuttōm t-tiru-t-tava-<unclear>t-tu</unclear>ṟai <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>varkku muttaiyil <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yōm
                    
                </p>
                <p>
                    Itu <unclear>pa</unclear><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>nm</unclear>āheśva<unclear>ra-rakṣai</unclear></hi>   
                </p>
                
